@startuml
' 图5-1 贝叶斯平滑贡献度算法流程
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Times New Roman
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam activityBorderColor #3C5488
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #F5F7FA
skinparam startColor #00A087
skinparam endColor #E64B35
skinparam diamondBackgroundColor #FFF8E1
skinparam diamondBorderColor #E69F00

start
:获取小组成员列表;

:采集四通道过程性数据;

fork
  :Git提交\n(次数+增删行)|
fork again
  :项目日志\n(提交数量)|
fork again
  :AI问答\n(提问次数)|
fork again
  :自测成绩\n(正答率)|
end fork

:计算原始贡献分 S_i\n0.35×Git + 0.20×日志\n+ 0.25×(问答+自测) + 0.20×加分;

:找到小组最高分 S_max;

:贝叶斯平滑\nr_i = (S_i + C×prior)/(S_max + C)\nprior=1/n, C=50;

if (r_i 异常?) then (是)
  :标记人工审核;
else (否)
endif

:计算最终成绩\nScore = Score_group×r_i + Score_bonus;

:持久化存储并触发达成度重算;

stop
@enduml
